Package query_translation.sql.utilities_sql

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTranslation
    For classes that take a DecodedQuery object and convert to SQL, they should extend this class.
    ForEach
    Method for translating Cypher with FOREACH into SQL.
    InsertUtils
    Class of helpful utilities for translation classes that edit the database (such as inserting new data).
    MultipleRel
    Class for translating Cypher with multiple relationships to SQL.
    NoRels
    Class for translating Cypher with no relationships to SQL.
    ShortestPath
    Class for translating Cypher with the shortestPath function to SQL.
    SingleVar
    Class for translating Cypher with a single variable length path to SQL.
    SQLTranslate
    MAIN TRANSLATION UNIT FROM INTERMEDIATE TRANSLATION TO SQL.
    TranslateUtils
    Class with useful translation methods that can be used regardless of the type of Cypher query actually being translated.
    UnionSQL
    Class for creating correct SQL query when UNION/UNION ALL keyword is present in the original Cypher query.
    WithSQL
